data.description: This move-in-ready brick ranch is a true gem that has everything you need for comfortable living. From the moment you step inside, you'll notice the attention to detail and the numerous updates that make this home truly special. The 30-year architectural roof, installed in 2019, ensures long-lasting protection and peace of mind.The kitchen is a chef's dream, with newer cabinets and countertops that offer ample storage and workspace. The tiled areas in key spaces add a touch of elegance and are easy to maintain. The newer windows throughout the home not only enhance the aesthetic appeal but also contribute to energy efficiency.The Great Room is the heart of the home, featuring a bay window that fills the space with natural light and offers a picturesque view. It's theperfect spot for relaxing with family and friends or enjoying some quiet time.  One of the highlights of this home is the delightful sunroom. With its vaulted ceilings and abundant windows, it is a bright and inviting space. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or curling up with a good book while enjoying the beauty of the outdoors.  Step outside and you'll find a sizable private backyard, enclosed by sturdy cinder block walls. This provides the perfect setting for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying some tranquility. The practical powered work shed is a great addition for those who love DIY projects or need extra storage space.  The 4th bedroom, with its own exit door, offers versatile options. It can serve as a guest room, home office, or even a private retreat. The possibilities are endless.  This home offers the convenience of being just minutes away from shopping, restaurants, and hospitals. Running daily errands or seeking healthcare services has never been easier.  And here's the icing on the cake - no HOA! Enjoy the freedom to personalize your space and make it truly your own without any restrictions.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful home yours. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities of living in this fantastic property.
